{"type": "excalidraw", "version": 2, "source": "excalidraw-diagram-skill", "elements": [{"type": "rectangle", "id": "darkbg", "x": -4000, "y": -3000, "width": 10000, "height": 7500, "backgroundColor": "#1e1e2e", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeColor": "transparent", "strokeWidth": 0, "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100}, {"type": "text", "id": "title1", "x": 20, "y": 10, "width": 346, "height": 28, "text": "Step 03 핵심 개념 관계도", "fontSize": 20, "strokeColor": "#e5e5e5", "fontFamily": 2, "textAlign": "center", "verticalAlign": "middle", "opacity": 100}, {"type": "rectangle", "id": "box2", "x": 20, "y": 45, "width": 346.0, "height": 360, "backgroundColor": "#1e3a5f", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeColor": "#4a9eed", "strokeWidth": 2, "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "roundness": {"type": 3}}, {"type": "text", "id": "txt3", "x": 35, "y": 60, "width": 316, "height": 330, "text": "웹 렌더링 방식\nMPA → SPA(CSR) → SSR → SSG/ISR → RSC\nReact의 정체성\n라이브러리 (UI만 담당) ←  IoC로 프레임워크와 구분\n부족한 영역을 생태계가 보완\n라우팅  React Router, TanStack Router\n데이터  TanStack Query, SWR, Axios\n상태  Zustand, Redux Toolkit, Jotai\n폼  React Hook Form + Zod\n스타일  Tailwind CSS, CSS Modules\n타입  TypeScript\n테스트  Vitest, RTL, Playwright\n빌드/배포  Vite, Vercel, GitHub Actions\n메타 프레임워크 = React + 생태계 통합 패키지\nNext.js, Remix, Gatsby", "fontSize": 14, "strokeColor": "#e5e5e5", "fontFamily": 2, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "middle", "opacity": 100, "containerId": "box2"}], "appState": {"viewBackgroundColor": "#1e1e2e"}}